Package com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.workload

The com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.workload package provides interfaces to configure workload network of a Supervisor.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Network
    Network class represents configuration for a network running workloads on a Supervisor.
    Network.Builder
    Builder class for Network.
    NetworkType
    NetworkType enumerates types of networks supported by the Supervisor for workloads.
    NsxNetwork
    NsxNetwork specifies network backing configuration that is specific to the workload network.
    NsxNetwork.Builder
    Builder class for NsxNetwork.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.workload package.
    VSphereNetwork
    VSphereNetwork specifies workload network configuration that is specific to vSphere networks.
    VSphereNetwork.Builder
    Builder class for VSphereNetwork.
    WorkloadFactory
    WorkloadFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.workload package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
  • Enum Summary

    NetworkType.Values
    Native Java enum representing this enumeration class.
